== Heart Sync ==

Code to run a pulse sensor amped on a FIO V3 and see the pulses on a digital LED strip (like adafruit's LED Belt Kit).

Youtube video:  [http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6v_glU5x6Mk]

* PulseSensorFioBeltX2.ino - the base program; derived originally from Adafruit's LED Belt tests.
* LPD8806.cpp and LPD8806.h - digital strip support code
* Interrupt.ino - pulse sensor support code, modified for FIO

